injectables.name: InstantUiLibraryService

components.name: AppComponent
components.templateData:
<!-- root module <instant-ui> to leak global class styles. -->
<iu-root>
  <iu-button
    [loading]="true"
    modeType="highlight"
    text="Highlight"
    (onClick)="click()"
  ></iu-button>
  <iu-loading-spinner
    id="1"
    variant="highlight"
    sizeMode="xlarge"
  ></iu-loading-spinner>
</iu-root>

components.name: BaseButtonComponent
components.templateData: {{ disabledMessage }}

components.name: InstantUiLibraryComponent
LoadingSpinnerComponent

modules.name: AppModule
BaseButtonModule
ButtonModule
InstantUiLibraryModule
LoadingSpinnerModule
